word_mean_info__list.difference: 指罕见的现象或奇人、奇事。
一般指被认为是人力所办不到的奇异之事。
侧重异乎寻常，奇怪，从而使人好奇。
通常指使人惊奇的事迹、人物或景观，主要指人创造的奇迹。

word_group.brief_definition: 神奇的药物；特效药；特效治疗药物

bilingual.target: 手术过程中发生了奇迹。

bilingual.source: They are wishing for a miracle to happen.

bilingual.target: 她的康复速度之快简直是个奇迹。

bilingual.source: She sees with her own eyes the miracle happen.
bilingual.target: 她亲眼所见了奇迹发生。

bilingual.source: A miracle happed when they least expected it.
bilingual.target: 当他们最不期望时，奇迹发生了。

bilingual.source: It was a miracle that he survived the accident.
bilingual.target: 他在事故中幸存下来真是个奇迹。

bilingual.source: Winning the championship was nothing short of a miracle.
bilingual.target: 赢得冠军简直是一个奇迹。

bilingual.source: The so-called miracle cure turned out to be a sham.
bilingual.target: 所谓的奇迹疗法结果是一个骗局。

bilingual.source: The revival of this small town is an economic miracle.
bilingual.target: 这个小镇的复兴是个经济奇迹。

bilingual.source: The socalled miracle cure turned out to be a scam.
bilingual.target: 这种所谓的奇迹疗法结果是个骗局。

list.abstract: miracle（英[ˈmɪrək(ə)l]，美[ˈmɪrək(ə)l]）,英语单词。词性是名词，译为奇迹、神奇妙事、人间奇迹等，短语搭配如miracle drug（特效药）。例句有“A machine which was a miracle of design.（堪称设计奇迹的机器。）” miracle作为名词时，相关近义词有phenomenon，wonder。
《miracle》是一首由westlife演唱的歌曲。 这是与Westlife的歌曲《Beautiful In White》同时期在网上开始流传的歌曲，并没有被以任何官方形式发行。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh. And so the miracle of birth begins.
yingyinNormal.zh: 生命的奇迹开始了…

yingyinNormal.en: Why isn't that laser beam cutting through the paint? It's the Miracle Wax! It certainly is a miracle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 激光束为什么切不断烤漆？是奇迹蜡的关系。那绝对是一项奇迹。

yingyinNormal.en: Which means Oozma Kappa’s back in the games! It's a miracle!
yingyinNormal.zh: 这表示万事OK社能返回赛局，真是奇迹啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. Oh, my God. Hey. Look at that. That's a Christmas miracle!
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿。喔！我的天！瞧瞧这，这真是圣诞奇迹！

yingyinNormal.en: Now, let's assume, by some miracle, you actually catch a fish.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在我们假设奇迹降临，你真的钓上来一条鱼。

yingyinNormal.en: I asked for one more miracle. I asked you to stop being dead. I heard you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我求你再创造一次奇迹。我求你活过来。我都听到了。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't look so surprised, Mr. Wazowski. It would have taken a miracle for you to...
yingyinNormal.zh: 别一副惊讶状，华斯基先生，你们过关需要奇迹。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh wow, three hours and still no baby. The miracle of birth sure is a snooze fest.
yingyinNormal.zh: 三个小时还是没生，生产的奇迹的确让人很想打瞌睡。

yingyinNormal.en: They believe so much how much you believe. What you did on that Ridge is nothing short of miracle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们如此相信你有多坚信。你在山脊上的所为就是奇迹。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you ready for the miracle event? Well then, I give to you, the astounding Bengal tiger!
yingyinNormal.zh: 准备好一起见证奇迹了吗？稍安勿躁，马上呈上令你大开眼界的孟加拉虎。

yingyinNormal.en: Wow! Look at that. The car is on fire, yet somehow its expensive paint job is protected by the Miracle Wax.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你瞧瞧，车子起火了，可是它那昂贵的烤漆却被奇迹蜡保护得毫发无伤。

yingyinNormal.en: I was there. I saw a miracle delivered. A perfect little face crying up at me. Mad as thunder.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我当时在场。见证了奇迹的诞生。那个婴儿有着完美无缺的脸蛋。哭声如雷霆般响亮。

yingyinNormal.en: Whichever way you look, inside or outside, up or down, the Opera House is nothing less than an architectural miracle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 无论您怎样看，从内到外，从上到下，歌剧院都绝对是个建筑奇迹。

yingyinNormal.en: Mom, Dad, we need to turn them into the perfect family for the holidays. We're gonna need a Christmas miracle!
yingyinNormal.zh: 爸爸妈妈，我们要把他们变成适合过节的完美家庭。我们需要一个圣诞奇迹！

yingyinNormal.en: Both parties have been wrangling over entitlements for months. What makes you think a miracle's gonna happen in the next three days?
yingyinNormal.zh: 两党在津贴上僵持数月了，你凭什么觉得接下来三天能出现奇迹呢？

yingyinNormal.en: We've got to make a play for Ruth Eastman. She's the miracle worker of Iowa, and she won't work with Hillary.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们得把鲁斯·伊斯曼拉拢过来，她是爱荷华的奇迹制造者，而且她不会帮希拉里做事。

yingyinNormal.en: Are they gonna get us a tow truck in there? Yes, baby, because it's a Thanksgiving miracle! Come on. Yay. Come on.
yingyinNormal.zh: 上那能给我们找辆拖车吗？可以的，宝贝，这可是感恩节的奇迹。来吧，太棒了。快来。

yingyinNormal.en: Yee haw! It's a miracle!
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘢哈! 梦一样的生活!

yingyinNormal.en: And if by certain I don't know miracle chance you survive you won't be giving no thanks to God.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如有某些我所不知的奇遇你活下来，你不会把感谢给上帝。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, I gotta tell you, those eye drops are a miracle. My eye is a 100% better. They're still in my coat. Damn.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那眼药水实在是太神奇了，我的眼睛百分之百好了。眼药水还放在我的外套里。可恶。
